This is a React based App which is backward and cross-browser compatible.
User will enter the location in the search field and the weather forecast information is displayed.
The widget then provides a list of potential sports that the user could engage in that would  be appropriate for the current weather conditions in the location they entered.
Widget uses AJAX to get data from the Open Weather Map.Creating the Ajax request with the Fetch API.
JQuery is used for animation.
Transpiled the ES6 code to ES5 using BABEL (Babel extension in Visual Studio Code)
Included Polyfills for Fetch API and Promise to make it work in the older browsers.
